WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:00.864
SMOKE PANEL!

00:00.864 --> 00:01.296
Golda

00:01.296 --> 00:04.272
emerges, a cigarette

00:04.272 --> 00:05.712
glowing fiercely.

00:05.712 --> 00:06.432
She

00:06.432 --> 00:08.448
commands, her voice

00:08.448 --> 00:08.928
gravelly:

00:08.928 --> 00:09.888
"I am

00:09.888 --> 00:13.368
the only man

00:13.368 --> 00:14.502
in the cabinet!

00:14.502 --> 00:14.880
"

00:14.880 --> 00:15.352
TRANSFORMATION!

00:15.352 --> 00:16.296
Cabinet members

00:16.296 --> 00:19.344
shrink to toddlers,

00:19.344 --> 00:20.568
their debates childish

00:20.568 --> 00:20.880
cries.

00:20.880 --> 00:21.504
Action explodes:

00:21.504 --> 00:23.136
Yom Kippur War!

00:23.136 --> 00:24.552
Coffee pot in

00:24.552 --> 00:25.944
one hand, tank

00:25.944 --> 00:27.192
radio in the

00:27.192 --> 00:27.728
other.

00:27.728 --> 00:28.264
KABOOM!

00:28.264 --> 00:28.800
SNAP!

00:28.800 --> 00:30.016
Intelligence failure!

00:30.016 --> 00:30.624
Crucial

00:30.624 --> 00:31.792
files scatter;

00:31.792 --> 00:32.376
warnings

00:32.376 --> 00:32.776
ignored.

00:32.776 --> 00:33.576
TIME REWIND:

00:33.576 --> 00:35.280
Ignored warnings flash.

00:35.280 --> 00:36.720
Kitchen diplomacy begins.

00:36.720 --> 00:38.088
World leaders shrink

00:38.088 --> 00:38.568
before her.

00:38.568 --> 00:38.808
Resignation!

00:38.808 --> 00:39.109
A mushroom cloud billows.

00:39.109 --> 00:39.334
The internet ignites.

00:39.334 --> 00:39.635
"There is no Palestine!

00:39.635 --> 00:39.786
" POW!

00:39.786 --> 00:39.936
Digital firestorm.

